                                                        <h2
                                                            class="coh-heading ssa-component coh-component ssa-component-instance-16fbe3c9-cac8-4175-87dc-11371ef1f237 coh-component-instance-16fbe3c9-cac8-4175-87dc-11371ef1f237  light-heading align-text-left coh-style-cfa-margin-bottom-lg     ssa-instance-9a7f77c8f24f88c5c4aa8aa14a3fd793 coh-ce-cpt_heading-b45c50fc">
                                                            Professional Journey
                                                        </h2>
                                                        <h3 style="color: #fff; font-weight:500; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"
                                                            class="coh-heading coh-style-headline-500 ssa-instance-c96d9abd7172c9cd49d5a55670f989d9 coh-ce-cpt_icon_card-d94f8b1f">
                                                            Early Beginnings</h3>
                                                        <div
                                                            class="coh-wysiwyg ssa-component coh-component ssa-component-instance-f21ab005-3355-4abe-96d4-588952153427 coh-component-instance-f21ab005-3355-4abe-96d4-588952153427  coh-style-text-color-dark-background       coh-style-cfa-margin-bottom-md    ssa-instance-7ab6e112073df199a5e217fffd6a6d3d coh-ce-cpt_text-e4a5f5e1">
                                                            <p>My passion for auditing and finance was ignited during my
                                                                B.Com studies, where I excelled in the subject of Auditing.
                                                                Encouraged by a friend, I joined a Chartered Accountancy
                                                                firm for an internship, which evolved into a full-fledged
                                                                career. Qualifying as a Chartered Accountant solidified my
                                                                belief that there are no shortcuts in life — only hard work
                                                                leads to success.
                                                                <br />
                                                                <br />
                                                                My first professional role was as an internal auditor at
                                                                CresBank, Pakistan’s first investment bank. I quickly
                                                                advanced to become the youngest CFO, Equity Strategist, and
                                                                Treasurer in the investment banking sector. However, my
                                                                desire to delve deeper into financial markets led me to
                                                                transition into corporate finance and equity strategy,
                                                                relocating to Karachi, Pakistan’s financial hub.
                                                                <br />
                                                                <br />
                                                            </p>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <h3 style="color: #fff; font-weight:500; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"
                                                            class="coh-heading coh-style-headline-500 ssa-instance-c96d9abd7172c9cd49d5a55670f989d9 coh-ce-cpt_icon_card-d94f8b1f">
                                                            Leadership Roles</h3>
                                                        <div
                                                            class="coh-wysiwyg ssa-component coh-component ssa-component-instance-f21ab005-3355-4abe-96d4-588952153427 coh-component-instance-f21ab005-3355-4abe-96d4-588952153427  coh-style-text-color-dark-background       coh-style-cfa-margin-bottom-md    ssa-instance-7ab6e112073df199a5e217fffd6a6d3d coh-ce-cpt_text-e4a5f5e1">
                                                            <p>I later joined PICIC, heading the Mutual Fund Division, where
                                                                I managed 14 closed-ended mutual funds acquired from the
                                                                Investment Corporation of Pakistan (ICP). My contributions
                                                                during this period were recognized as exceptional, both by
                                                                my standards and by those of a highly experienced board.
                                                                <br />
                                                                <br />
                                                                I worked as a domestic consultant for the Asian Development
                                                                Bank (ADB), an experience that deepened my understanding of
                                                                financial consultancy and shattered many preconceived
                                                                notions about the consultants.
                                                                <br />
                                                                <br />
                                                            </p>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <h3 style="color: #fff; font-weight:500; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"
                                                            class="coh-heading coh-style-headline-500 ssa-instance-c96d9abd7172c9cd49d5a55670f989d9 coh-ce-cpt_icon_card-d94f8b1f">
                                                            Joining AKD Securities</h3>
                                                        <div
                                                            class="coh-wysiwyg ssa-component coh-component ssa-component-instance-f21ab005-3355-4abe-96d4-588952153427 coh-component-instance-f21ab005-3355-4abe-96d4-588952153427  coh-style-text-color-dark-background       coh-style-cfa-margin-bottom-md    ssa-instance-7ab6e112073df199a5e217fffd6a6d3d coh-ce-cpt_text-e4a5f5e1">
                                                            <p>In a pivotal moment of my career, I was invited by the
                                                                legendary Aqeel Karim Dhedhi (AKD) to join AKD Group. I
                                                                embraced the opportunity, eventually becoming the CEO of AKD
                                                                Securities. Here, I found my passion for capital markets,
                                                                navigating the dynamic world of equity trading and
                                                                investment banking.
                                                                <br />
                                                                <br />
                                                            </p>
                                                        </div>
